        {
            "title": "堪薩斯聯儲行長：進一步降息可能加劇美國通膨壓力",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Kansas City Fed President Jeffrey Schmid.\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rZVw8i8hwgjyaWrejEApOQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/ac7ce6d074d1818b011499558dc98af6\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Kansas City Fed President Jeffrey Schmid.</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 堪薩斯城聯邦儲備銀行行長Jeff Schmid表示，進一步降息可能會加深高通膨風險，而非有效支撐勞動力市場。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Schmid周五在丹佛的一次演講中說：「我認為進一步降息並不會對修補勞動力市場的裂縫產生多大作用，這些壓力更可能源於技術和移民政策帶來的結構性變化。然而，降息可能會對通膨產生更持久的影響，因為外界對我們實現2%目標的承諾將越來越存疑。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Schmid表示，這一考量正引導他為聯儲會12月政策會議作準備，但他也補充稱，未來幾周仍會根據新數據調整看法。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-14aa87ce-c74c-39c4-a63d-fea1226d9f2c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"堪薩斯州城聯邦聯儲會行長傑弗裡·施密德。攝影：David Paul Morris/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ewzYWQojERoC5u.Z4sjZtg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/32bb3e5f87d08200ac785e06b2f17994\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">堪薩斯州城聯邦聯儲會行長傑弗裡·施密德。攝影：David Paul Morris/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">過去兩次會議，聯儲會均降息以支撐近幾個月明顯放緩的就業市場。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Schmid在10月的會議上投票反對降息，主張維持利率不變，並認為經濟成長依然強勁，可能重新點燃通膨壓力。他周五重申，目前利率僅對經濟造成溫和壓力，他認為這「恰到好處」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「讓人擔心的不僅僅是關稅，甚至主要問題也不是關稅，」他說，「我聽到很多關於醫療費用和保險保費上升的擔憂，聽到不少關於電價上漲的意見。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Fed’s Schmid Says More Cuts Could Drive Inflation Pressures</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A0%AA%E8%96%A9%E6%96%AF%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E8%A1%8C%E9%95%B7-%E9%80%B2-%E6%AD%A5%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%A0%E5%8A%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%80%9A%E8%86%A8%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B-154352034.html",
